title: Founders’ 5K Fun Run at Barry University
text:
Founders’ 5K Fun Run at Barry University Where 
9:00 a.m. Saturday, Nov. 14, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, On Campus | Alumni Founders’ 5K Fun Run (formerly known as the Gobble Wobble) is designed and carried out by students in the Department of Sport and Exercise Sciences. This promises to be a fun morning for the whole family. We look forward to seeing you there! WHO does it benefit? FLIPANY: Florida Introduces Physical Activity and Nutrition to Youth. A local non-for-profit organization that promotes the consumption of nutritious foods and physical activity to youth. (www.flipany.org) Includes entry fee, t-shirt & breakfast Barry Students: $15 Barry Faculty, Staff & Alumni: $30 Community Members: $35 Family rate: $75 for 3 participants ($5 for each additional person- must register at the same time)
